# AgentFlow 系统架构图

## 整体架构

```mermaid
graph TB
    subgraph Frontend["前端表达层 (React + TypeScript)"]
        WF["工作流画布<br/>(ReactFlow)"]
        NP["节点配置面板<br/>(Ant Design)"]
        MON["执行监控<br/>(SSE实时推送)"]
        LOG["日志查看<br/>(Monaco Editor)"]
    end

    subgraph Console["控制台中枢层 (Console Hub - Java / 8081)"]
        AUTH["用户鉴权<br/>(Spring Security)"]
        MODEL["模型管理<br/>(Spring AI)"]
        META["流程元数据<br/>(MyBatis-Plus)"]
        DISPATCH["执行调度<br/>(REST/SSE)"]
    end

    subgraph Workflow["Java 工作流引擎 (7880)"]
        subgraph Executor["核心执行器 (NodeExecutor)"]
            START["Start<br/>Executor"]
            LLM["LLM<br/>Executor"]
            PLUGIN["Plugin<br/>Executor"]
            IFELSE["If-Else<br/>Executor"]
        end
        
        VP["VariablePool<br/>变量池"]
        DSL["WorkflowDSL<br/>DSL解析"]
    end

    subgraph Infra["基础设施层"]
        MYSQL["MySQL"]
        REDIS["Redis"]
        MINIO["MinIO"]
        NGINX["Nginx"]
    end

    Frontend -->|"HTTP/SSE"| Console
    Console -->|"REST"| Workflow
    Workflow --> Infra

    style Frontend fill:#e6e6fa,stroke:#667eea
    style Console fill:#e8f8f5,stroke:#11998e
    style Workflow fill:#fff5e6,stroke:#fc4a1a
    style Infra fill:#e8ecf0,stroke:#45637a
```

## 工作流执行流程

```mermaid
flowchart LR
    subgraph Request["用户请求"]
        USER["用户发起请求"]
    end

    subgraph Hub["Console Hub (8081)"]
        AUTH1["鉴权验证"]
        LOAD["加载DSL"]
        VERIFY["验证配置"]
        FORWARD["转发请求"]
        SSE["SSE推送"]
        RESP["返回结果"]
    end

    subgraph Engine["Workflow Engine (7880)"]
        PARSE["DSL解析"]
        BUILD["链路构建"]
        LOOP["环路检测"]
        EXEC["节点执行"]
        CALLBACK["回调通知"]
    end

    USER --> AUTH1
    AUTH1 --> LOAD --> VERIFY --> FORWARD --> SSE --> RESP
    FORWARD -->|"HTTP POST"| PARSE
    PARSE --> BUILD --> LOOP
    LOOP -->|"无环"| EXEC
    EXEC --> CALLBACK
    CALLBACK -->|"SSE Stream"| SSE

    style Request fill:#e6f0ff,stroke:#4facfe
    style Hub fill:#e8f8f5,stroke:#11998e
    style Engine fill:#fff5e6,stroke:#fc4a1a
```

## 节点执行流程

```mermaid
flowchart TB
    subgraph Input["输入处理"]
        RESOLVE["resolveInputs()<br/>解析模板变量"]
        TEMPLATE["{{node-llm::002.output}}"]
    end

    subgraph Execute["节点执行"]
        EXEC_NODE["executeNode()<br/>执行业务逻辑"]
        LLM_CALL["LLM调用/插件执行"]
    end

    subgraph Output["输出处理"]
        STORE["storeOutputs()<br/>保存到变量池"]
        OUTPUT["node-id.output-name"]
    end

    subgraph Callback["回调通知"]
        CB["callback.onNodeEnd()<br/>通知工作流"]
    end

    RESOLVE --> TEMPLATE --> EXEC_NODE
    EXEC_NODE --> LLM_CALL --> STORE
    STORE --> OUTPUT --> CB

    style Input fill:#f0f4ff,stroke:#667eea
    style Execute fill:#fff5e6,stroke:#fc4a1a
    style Output fill:#e8f8f5,stroke:#11998e
    style Callback fill:#e8ecf0,stroke:#45637a
```

## VariablePool 变量池

```mermaid
graph LR
    subgraph Pool["VariablePool"]
        subgraph Node1["spark-llm::002"]
            O1["output: 'AI回答'"]
            R1["reason: '思考过程'"]
